Detailed Description

Error condition debug. After an error is detected by the CSIRX, this register indicates which virtual channel, datatype and data field is impacted.

Field Documentation

Indicates the Data Field for an invalid CRC/ECC/Data ID

Indicates the Data Type for a invalid CRC/ECC/Data ID
